l?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9f9ty1Q.jpg&h=93c9aed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWOFp8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWOFp8w.jpg&h=27fc9018&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77ba3bd5b55227f5bc062cd80a0cfd7c06c04647","tid":1057332,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"成個trip應該要用幾多錢?巴打辭工去旅行?"},{"pid":"83da57a10f048a4837112987470391e502141fb2","tid":1057332,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ba3bd5b55227f5bc062cd80a0cfd7c06c04647","tid":1057332,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"成個trip應該要用幾多錢?巴打辭工去旅行?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"去左19個國家，42日左右。(橙線)<br />\n大約暫時用左 HKD13,000左右 (未買回港機票)<br />\n<br />\n我未至於窮遊，但住同車都揀平既，一間房6張床果d。東歐比較平，平均7歐元一晚。<br />\ncity to city巴士10歐至20歐元一程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fhZmgwK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfhZmgwK.jpg&h=eb537f88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6889021352338608822833e7486d5ec39d4c53c8","tid":1057332,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"3個月唔會開始麻木咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己grad trip個半月，去到後期其實好多景點之類都覺得無所謂睇唔睇都得，思鄉就冇既，不過覺得冇左頭2個星期個種激動"},{"pid":"d4f4c66e6ef1d7b9a3d98c95ab00ac7f61da0197","tid":1057332,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6889021352338608822833e7486d5ec39d4c53c8","tid":1057332,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"3個月唔會開始麻木咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己grad trip個半月，去到後期其實好多景點之類都覺得無所謂睇唔睇都得，思鄉就冇既，不過覺得冇左頭2個星期個種激動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"我係一個好易悶既人，歐洲其實d野真係差唔多。<br />\n一開波去左幾十間教堂，而家見到教堂都冇感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg